28ac790d-6244-4486-832c-1d3e2e5dc817.question: How many singers do we have?
28ac790d-6244-4486-832c-1d3e2e5dc817.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

770c6b37-ce1c-42a4-acee-b7bfb1636f3d.question: List the name, country and age for all singers ordered by age from the oldest to the youngest.
770c6b37-ce1c-42a4-acee-b7bfb1636f3d.sql: SELECT name, country, age FROM singer ORDER BY age DESC
770c6b37-ce1c-42a4-acee-b7bfb1636f3d.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

8b0bdb0b-3804-4858-955a-b87a15fec575.question: What is the average, minimum, and maximum age of all singers from France?
8b0bdb0b-3804-4858-955a-b87a15fec575.sql: SELECT AVG(age), MIN(age), MAX(age) FROM singer WHERE country = 'France'
8b0bdb0b-3804-4858-955a-b87a15fec575.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

8815e25b-bbf0-491c-98e8-7c6c49935770.question: Show the distinct countries where singers above age 20 are from.
8815e25b-bbf0-491c-98e8-7c6c49935770.sql: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM singer WHERE age > 20
8815e25b-bbf0-491c-98e8-7c6c49935770.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

bdd28052-d014-406f-8345-fd95f3e6c9c8.question: How many singers do we have from each country?
bdd28052-d014-406f-8345-fd95f3e6c9c8.sql: SELECT country, COUNT(*) FROM singer GROUP BY country
bdd28052-d014-406f-8345-fd95f3e6c9c8.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

31ee7408-4d2c-43d7-a48c-b59c64375447.question: Show names of songs whose singer's age is older than the average age.
31ee7408-4d2c-43d7-a48c-b59c64375447.sql: SELECT song_name FROM singer WHERE age > (SELECT AVG(age) FROM singer)
31ee7408-4d2c-43d7-a48c-b59c64375447.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER), song_name (TEXT)

00375d1a-0f21-4ece-99bc-088692a01cef.question: Show the stadium name and the number of concerts in each stadium.
00375d1a-0f21-4ece-99bc-088692a01cef.sql: SELECT T2.name, COUNT(*) FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id GROUP BY T1.stadium_id
00375d1a-0f21-4ece-99bc-088692a01cef.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), concert_name (TEXT), stadium_id (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)

1b87eaad-ab38-4c1a-b519-52ab7c7afa56.question: Show the location and name of stadiums which have some concerts with capacity between 5000 and 10000.
1b87eaad-ab38-4c1a-b519-52ab7c7afa56.sql: SELECT location, name FROM stadium WHERE capacity BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000
1b87eaad-ab38-4c1a-b519-52ab7c7afa56.schema: Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), location (TEXT), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)

df0628af-4ad6-45fb-9e40-c5e57a2daa21.question: Show the stadium names without any concert.
df0628af-4ad6-45fb-9e40-c5e57a2daa21.sql: SELECT name FROM stadium WHERE stadium_id NOT IN (SELECT stadium_id FROM concert)
df0628af-4ad6-45fb-9e40-c5e57a2daa21.schema:
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER)

adda7a3c-2fe7-4d66-978d-ffaf750c5def.question: What are the countries that have both singers above age 40 and singers below age 30?
adda7a3c-2fe7-4d66-978d-ffaf750c5def.sql: SELECT country FROM singer WHERE age > 40 INTERSECT SELECT country FROM singer WHERE age < 30
adda7a3c-2fe7-4d66-978d-ffaf750c5def.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

ba07e847-d4ae-45c7-8f83-8dd1c8b0aa12.question: Show all birth years of singers from France or singers from USA.
ba07e847-d4ae-45c7-8f83-8dd1c8b0aa12.sql: SELECT birth_year FROM singer WHERE country = 'France' UNION SELECT birth_year FROM singer WHERE country = 'USA'
ba07e847-d4ae-45c7-8f83-8dd1c8b0aa12.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), birth_year (INTEGER)

7d811371-f45e-452c-a478-e25ff4e2a945.question: Find names of stadiums that did not have a concert in 2014.
7d811371-f45e-452c-a478-e25ff4e2a945.sql: SELECT name FROM stadium EXCEPT SELECT T2.name FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id WHERE T1.year = 2014
7d811371-f45e-452c-a478-e25ff4e2a945.schema:
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER), year (INTEGER)

c91705b1-4d99-48cf-bea8-bc0f5d9bc4cd.question: List all singers whose song name contains 'Hey'.
c91705b1-4d99-48cf-bea8-bc0f5d9bc4cd.sql: SELECT name FROM singer WHERE song_name LIKE '%Hey%'

c6eb8134-e102-4c87-8410-443b5da1a298.question: Find the first name and gender of students who have more than one pet.
c6eb8134-e102-4c87-8410-443b5da1a298.sql: SELECT T1.fname, T1.sex FROM student AS T1 JOIN has_pet AS T2 ON T1.stuid = T2.stuid GROUP BY T1.stuid HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
c6eb8134-e102-4c87-8410-443b5da1a298.schema:
Table student: stuid (INTEGER), fname (TEXT), sex (TEXT)
Table has_pet: stuid (INTEGER), petid (INTEGER)

d56011ee-2830-4d73-8010-9e8f6f0e1df3.question: Show names of singers who performed in concerts in 2014.
d56011ee-2830-4d73-8010-9e8f6f0e1df3.sql: SELECT T2.name FROM singer_in_concert AS T1 JOIN singer AS T2 ON T1.singer_id = T2.singer_id JOIN concert AS T3 ON T1.concert_id = T3.concert_id WHERE T3.year = 2014
d56011ee-2830-4d73-8010-9e8f6f0e1df3.schema:
Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table singer_in_concert: singer_id (INTEGER), concert_id (INTEGER)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), concert_name (TEXT), year (INTEGER)

4a143c07-7d5c-45e3-8204-5e27ac881053.question: Show the stadium name and capacity with highest average attendance.
4a143c07-7d5c-45e3-8204-5e27ac881053.sql: SELECT name, capacity FROM stadium ORDER BY average DESC LIMIT 1
4a143c07-7d5c-45e3-8204-5e27ac881053.schema: Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER), average (REAL)

51cf86d6-196a-4b37-af39-142d481920c3.question: How many concerts are there in 2014 or 2015?
51cf86d6-196a-4b37-af39-142d481920c3.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM concert WHERE year = 2014 OR year = 2015

a6558922-e693-44ff-af2e-e071d22958fd.question: Show stadium name and capacity for the stadium with most concerts after 2013, and sort by the number of concerts in descending order.
a6558922-e693-44ff-af2e-e071d22958fd.sql: SELECT T2.name, T2.capacity FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id WHERE T1.year > 2013 GROUP BY T2.stadium_id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1
a6558922-e693-44ff-af2e-e071d22958fd.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER), year (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)

d830b8dc-9ab1-45bd-b4e2-a2d1c6dfe676.question: How many concerts occurred in the stadium with the largest capacity?
d830b8dc-9ab1-45bd-b4e2-a2d1c6dfe676.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM concert WHERE stadium_id = (SELECT stadium_id FROM stadium ORDER BY capacity DESC LIMIT 1)
d830b8dc-9ab1-45bd-b4e2-a2d1c6dfe676.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), capacity (INTEGER)

53faf836-edbe-4b94-be42-3c311b208253.question: Find the maximum and minimum weight for each pet type.
53faf836-edbe-4b94-be42-3c311b208253.sql: SELECT MAX(weight), pettype FROM pets GROUP BY pettype
